    Product Description

    Style:Privacy/Bathroom

    Whether for industrial, medical, office or commercial spaces, Lynn locksets are here when you need it most. Excellent replacement/upgrading option and for use in Medium to High Traffic facilities such as Schools, Government Buildings, Retail, Office, Medical Facilities, Hospitals, Libraries, Hotels, Airports, Multi-Family Buildings, Condos.

    Cold Rolled Steel machined and threaded hubs and locking nuts - securely bolt the chassis to the door thereby preventing loosening the lockset even with hundreds of uses per day.

    Specifications:
    --NON-HANDED (fits both Right Hand and Left Hand Doors)
    --For Doors 1-3/8 to 1-3/4 (35mm to 44mm)
    --Backset 2-3/4 (70mm)
    --Front Stainless Steel, 2-1/4 x 1-1/8 (57mm x 29mm)
    --Strike ANSI (4-7/8 x 1-1/4)
    --Roses 3-3/8 (90mm) Diameter Stainless steel
    --Fits 161 door prep --Latchbolt Stainless steel 1/2 (12.5mm) throw standard

    In box:
    --1 Cylindrical Lockset - Privacy Function (The outside lever is locked by pushing a button on the inside and can be unlocked from the outside by using a flat object (coin or screwdriver) to turn the button for emergency entrance. Also, Turning inside lever or closing the door will release the button. Inside lever is always free for immediate egress.
    --Mounting Screws and bolts
    --User Friendly Instructions & Template
    --1 ANSI Strike
    --1 Reversible Latch Unit

    Warranty: 10 years

    Certification:
    --ANSI/BHMA Certified A156.2 - Grade 2 (exceeds 400,000 cycles)
    --ADA Compliant A117.10
    --cUL/UL Listed - 3 Hours

    How are ratings calculated?
    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
